ygData.msgSnippet: Actually, the only problem I had in Freeport was the northern sectors, those pesky paladins didn t care for me too much, unfortunately that s where the bank is
ygData.messageBody:
Actually, the only problem I had in Freeport was the northern sectors, those
pesky paladins didn't care for me too much, unfortunately that's where the
bank is as well, and there isn't a blackburrow type area in which to quickly
raise faction..slaying orc pawns in the newbie zone isn't my idea of a good
time :)

continent. Not to mention Dark Elf Necros can go into East Freeport without
being attacked.

Naeeldar Level 22 Necromancer
